articles.title: Welcome to Visual Analytics and Applications!
articles.description: Welcome to the website. This hosts the write up of **Archie Dolit** for DataViz Makeovers, Invididual Assignments, Group Projects and In-Class Exercises of [ISSS608 Visual Analytics and Applications](https://isss608.netlify.app/). Additionally, it also includes various topics discussed in [GeoSpatial Data Science and Analytics](https://geodsa.netlify.app/)!
